{"tid":522492,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原 子 鏸 與 外 籍 男 友 訂 婚","createTime":"2018-01-07T15:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T17:01:50.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52ed632c30f0e62c8960aa2244b0b255184dca30","tid":522492,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"原子鏸（Marsha）跟外籍男友Mehdi交往不經不覺已經一年多，日前她跟母親鄭佩佩及家人到歐洲男友家度假，順便慶祝佩佩姐72歲生日。想不到男友為Marsha製造驚喜，當着眾人面前下跪求婚，前日佩佩姐在微博貼出當日求婚的照片，跟fans分享喜訊。照片中男友的家人以手機拍攝求婚過程，見到相中Marsha驚喜交集的神情。<br />\n<br />\n昨日佩佩姐透過助手回覆表示：「一家仲喺歐洲男仔屋企，每年1月6日生日，一家都會一齊過，今年就去咗Marsha男友屋企過。求婚一事事前大家都唔知，好surprise、好開心。𠵱家只係訂婚，同男仔拍咗一年幾拖。」佩佩姐透露昨日舉家將轉往英國繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180104/large/04ec2p7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180104%2Flarge%2F04ec2p7e.jpg&h=c0a947d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bbe504fe80c15ee46f59672d1d00edbe7b76569","tid":522492,"uid":165875,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:48:12.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},{"pid":"0773d06488224c91bdbfa50c128c1f59e6e6b4be","tid":522492,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bbe504fe80c15ee46f59672d1d00edbe7b76569","tid":522492,"uid":165875,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:48:12.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"男親女愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cce1f72620ce4741fafbf3d2221db410440739c","tid":522492,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"阮阮"},{"pid":"8b900d26532693af311450c30e52709c63ed3a93","tid":522492,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0773d06488224c91bdbfa50c128c1f59e6e6b4be","tid":522492,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bbe504fe80c15ee46f59672d1d00edbe7b76569","tid":522492,